description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 33, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 264, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 1 for East, 2 for South, and Stringalong for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50338-91272-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [264 Votes, Top 5% Score]
